# Scrum Sprint Diagrams

## Sprint Cycle
```mermaid
graph TD
    PB[Product Backlog] --> SP[Sprint Planning]
    SP --> SB[Sprint Backlog]
    SB --> Daily[Daily Scrum]
    Daily --> |Every Day| Daily
    Daily --> Review[Sprint Review]
    Review --> Retro[Sprint Retrospective]
    Retro --> PB
    
    style Daily fill:#90EE90
```

## Sprint Timeline
```mermaid
gantt
    title Sprint 15 (2 Weeks)
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    
    section Ceremonies
    Sprint Planning      :done, plan, 2025-07-07, 4h
    Daily Standups       :active, daily, after plan, 10d
    Sprint Review        :review, 2025-07-18, 2h
    Sprint Retrospective :retro, after review, 2h
    
    section Development
    Story 1 (5 pts)      :done, s1, 2025-07-08, 3d
    Story 2 (3 pts)      :active, s2, after s1, 2d
    Story 3 (8 pts)      :s3, 2025-07-10, 5d
    Story 4 (5 pts)      :s4, after s2, 3d
```

## Burndown Chart Concept
```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Sprint Burndown"
        A[40 pts] -->|Day 1| B[38 pts]
        B -->|Day 2| C[35 pts]
        C -->|Day 3| D[32 pts]
        D -->|Day 4| E[28 pts]
        E -->|Day 5| F[24 pts - Current]
        F -.->|Projected| G[20 pts]
        G -.->|Day 10| H[0 pts]
    end
    
    style F fill:#90EE90
```

